Prompt:

Create a single-slide Azure Cloud Infrastructure Overview on a white background with a Segoe UI font and Azure brand colors (primary blue #0078D4). Use a gradient blue-to-navy top bar on the slide master and a thin blue bottom accent line.

Layout the slide as an 8-section dashboard grid — 4 sections on top, 4 on bottom — each with a colored rounded-rectangle header and a bordered card below containing component details. Use these sections and colors:

NETWORKING (Azure Blue #0078D4) — VNet 10.0.0.0/16, 4 subnets (Frontend 10.0.1.0/24 with App Gateway + WAF, Backend 10.0.2.0/24 with AKS + VMs, Data 10.0.3.0/24 with SQL + Redis + Cosmos, Mgmt 10.0.4.0/24 with Bastion + Jump Box), NSG Rules, Azure Firewall Premium. Show subnets as a 2×2 grid of light-blue cards inside a blue-bordered VNet container.
