SECURITY & IDENTITY (Red, darken header to #B71C2E for contrast) — Entra ID Premium P2 (MFA, PIM, Conditional Access, RBAC, JIT, B2C 50K MAU, SAML/OIDC SSO). Two cards: Key Vault (Premium HSM, auto-rotation) and Defender for Cloud (CSPM + CWP, Enhanced Security). Bottom strip: DDoS Protection Standard, Private Endpoints, Service Endpoints.
DEVOPS & CI/CD (Purple #7B5EA7) — Azure DevOps + GitHub Actions, 25 repos, YAML pipelines, 12 self-hosted build agents, NuGet + npm + Docker artifacts via ACR, Blue/Green + Canary + Feature Flags releases, Terraform + Bicep + ARM IaC.
MONITORING & OBSERVABILITY (Orange, darken header to #B06000 for contrast) — Azure Monitor + Log Analytics, Application Insights APM, 90-day retention, 150+ alert rules + Action Groups + PagerDuty, Grafana + Azure Workbooks dashboards, Network Watcher + Traffic Analytics + Flow Logs.
AI/ML & MESSAGING (Azure Blue #0078D4) — Azure OpenAI (GPT-4 Turbo, Embeddings, DALL-E 3), Azure ML workspace + compute clusters, Cognitive Services (Vision, Speech, Language), Service Bus Premium, Event Hub Standard, Event Grid, Azure Functions Consumption.
GOVERNANCE & COST (Navy #1B2A4A) — 3 Subscriptions (Prod/Staging/Dev), 85 Azure Policy assignments + CIS Benchmark, Cost Management with budgets + alerts + Reserved Instances, Tags (Env/Owner/CostCenter/Project), Blueprints + Landing Zones + CAF aligned.
Add a dark navy (#1B2A4A) rounded-rectangle footer bar spanning the full width with white text: "Region: East US (Primary) + West US (DR) | SLA Target: 99.95% | RPO: 15min / RTO: 1hr | Est. Monthly Cost: ~$45,000 | Resources: 180+"

Top-right corner: "☁ Microsoft Azure" in blue as a brand label. Title at top-left: "Azure Cloud Infrastructure Overview" in 22pt blue bold, with a subtitle line below: "Production Environment | Enterprise Architecture | Multi-Region Deployment" in 9pt gray.

Use light-tinted backgrounds in each card matching its section color. All detail text 5.5–7pt in gray (#5A6A7A), headers/labels in bold in darker shades of each section color. Keep everything on one slide with no empty space at the bottom.


